After just reading on Hacker News about Google&rsquo;s newly released TensorFlow library , for deep learning based on tensors and data flow, I realized I wrote in a draft post back in 2013 that:
&ldquo;What if one could have a fully declarative &ldquo;matrix language&rdquo; in which all data transformations ever needed could be declaratively defined in a way that is very easy to comprehend?&rdquo;
&hellip; so, I thought this is a good time to post this draft, to see whether it spurs any further ideas.
